properties.Name: FluidCatalyticCrackerUnitProduction
properties.Description:
The quantity of product produced by the FCCU during the associated period.

Ex:
-  Light gas -H2, C1, and C2s
-  LPG C3s and C4s - includes light olefins
-  Gasoline C5+ high octane 
-  Light cycle oil (LCO)  
-  Heavy cycle oil (HCO)  
-  Clarified oil (CLO) 
-  Coke
